Mary R Stauffer Foundation
September 14, 2019 at 1:18 PM ·

The Stauffer Foundation invites ALL DUSD families to the College Savings Plan meeting on Monday 9.16 @ 7pm at the District Office. There will be raffles and refreshments AND Dr. Stauffer will be in attendance. Please come by if you’re thinking about getting started with your college savings plan. {please feel free to share this post on your FB page}
